snippet.title: Plague of the Moon (DOS) - Playthrough/Longplay
snippet.description:
If you ever plan on saving on something within a shovelware disc, make sure you extract the game off the disc first or tension goes from 5 MPH to 80MPH very quickly. 

It was going to be a short gameplay video, but then I went rogue and did a full Longplay. As of right now the full version is currently lost unless Gabe Macchia is actually alive still and has a copy in some attic, we will never know if our expectations of bad voice acting would be met or if the uncensored deaths are worthy enough to make a "Ways to Die" video.
